Groundwork director, Bobby Peek speaks to #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Environmental Justice Group is celebrating a victory following the judgment in the 'Deadly Air' case. The High Court has recognised the poor air quality in Mpumalanga, Highveld region as a breach of residents’ Constitutional right to an environment that is not harmful to their health and well-being. Groundwork director, Bobby Peek speaks to eNCA in the video above. 